Text: This is an attempt to help spread educational materials to circumvent the efforts of Anti P2P organizations.
instead of trying to "fool" TPB why not take it to the forum?
I didn't know there was a forum.  I just wanted to get the message seen, wasn't trying to break the rules, just bend them.

Oh, Supr.  I reported a few bad torrents there, but that site is far too broad in subject matter to expect a simple text file of info to be viewed, especially since many TPB users aren't aware of its existence.
